{
  "stem": "471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And later, they said that they brought-- they brought-- they [INAUDIBLE] camp, and they brought him over here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But anyway, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] as they build the barrack, and that they built the fence around the camp, on the top there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "On the top.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And-- and they developed what they called that Hujowa Gorka, the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they were making different projects.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You know, different trades, they were working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They had all the trades there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] One fine day, a new-- a new commandant came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They liquidate Julag down there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Miller was out, they sent him on the front.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And the new commandant came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And here came the monster, Otto Goth-- I think Otto Goth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "My God, when I saw him the first time-- just for looking at him [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was unbearable.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It's unbelievable, what a brutal man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He just ate an apple here and then pow, pow, pow-- shot people like-- like nothing, for no reason.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The same time, Hujowa Gorka was developed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "You known, Hujowa Gorka is that place where it's mass graves, mass graves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Over there, they brought the body.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They dump them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[SPEAKING POLISH]-- it means like a Caterpillar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "You know, a big truck would-- would pick up the dirt and just throw it on there, that's it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "The way you're found.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They were clothed, not clothed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "That's the way they were dead, laying there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The next-- the next people from there, they liquidate the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From all the ghetto, they shoot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of the times, they killed the people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Before the deportation-- excuse me, when I was in the Julag, there was a deportation in the ghetto, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father was shot in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
